[[File:Reward casket (easy) detail.png|left|130px]]
A '''[[reward casket]] (easy)''' is received after completing the final clue of an [[Clue scroll (easy)|easy clue scroll]] trail, and contains the final reward for the trail. In addition to items listed below, various elemental and higher level runes can be received as part of an easy clue scroll reward.

While players can only have one of each type of clue scroll in their possession, they can possess unlimited amounts of reward caskets, and are eligible to receive clue scrolls again once it is obtained.

==Rewards==
Easy clues generate a minimum of 2 rewards and a maximum of 4, granting an average of 3 rewards per casket. The rewards consist of generic items, shared treasure trail items and items that are unique for easy clues. Additionally, players have a 1/50 chance to receive a [[master clue scroll]] upon opening an easy casket.

All droprates are confirmed by Mod Tide.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Tide|url=https://twitter.com/JagexTide/status/1131933683714330624|date=24 May 2019|archiveurl=https://archive.fo/WUqwD|archivedate=24 May 2019|quote=I know its been a while since the clue expansion but here is the information on clue scroll drop rates and loot chances! If anything changes I will keep you posted.|name=Clue rates tweet}}{{CiteGeneral|url=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16pVNHdZyynmxIbM9mynRDYT0LQsWxq-vbDs4_7DpnGM/edit?usp=sharing|title=Clue scrolls 2019|author=|time=24 May 2019}} The listed rarities are per roll.

The average loot roll is worth {{Coins|floor({{EasyClueValue}})}}. On average, easy clues are worth {{Coins|floor(3 * {{EasyClueValue}})}}. The 1/50 chance of receiving a master clue scroll adds another {{Coins|floor(1/50 * 6 * {{MasterClueValue}})}}, for a total expected value per clue of {{Coins|floor(3 * {{EasyClueValue}} + 1/50 * 6 * {{MasterClueValue}})}}.

The probability to receive a clue scroll unique item from an easy casket is 247/1080, or roughly 22.9%. <ref>The chance for a unique is 1151/14040 per roll, with an average of 3 rolls per easy casket. </ref>

